{"tid":1407444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府呼籲市民一同向暴力說「不」","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:36:52.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b77c7f2969e0b1f58829b5dd66bfef4cc4c32be9","tid":1407444,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"政府發言人就今天（八月四日）在將軍澳、西區及銅鑼灣的示威活動作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n　　繼昨天（八月三日）及今天凌晨在油尖旺及黃大仙等地區出現違法及暴力示威活動後，今天自下午起有示威者惡意破壞將軍澳警署、在西區堵路；到晚上大批示威者在銅鑼灣一帶集結，再次堵塞紅磡海底隧道出入口、破壞警車和交通燈、襲擊警務人員以至縱火。今天的惡劣情況再次顯示暴力及違法示威正在不斷擴散，正將香港推向極為危險的邊緣，特區政府予以強烈譴責。我們呼籲市民一同向暴力說「不」，讓社會盡快回復秩序。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月4日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間23時22分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af637869fa64da92f5b1f76196fffb6e2c843224","tid":1407444,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f10414d28fe4058fb4234ca51d73f76cf26ac0","tid":1407444,"uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"向暴力說不<br />\n所以要制止警方濫權<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a593112a75b8e7a3ebfce980576ae8328dbc510","tid":1407444,"uid":40628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:29:53.000Z","msg":"譴責完就無人抗議, 一天都光晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個政府仲要發撚緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa638e1a142075d73f4e87aeb0b41c242e68650","tid":1407444,"uid":5945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"向狗說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\